ygData.messageBody:
Cazic thule would be a very good place to go. you can stay there thru 35th
if you see fit to do so, beware there are lots of trains but dont worry just
zone out and then back. the exp is good and the fs weapons can make you
some cash.

Kizmet Bayashi
Monk of the 48th ..
E-Marr
Da`Kor
